  <title>Switch on/off based on the clap sound</title>
  <subsection xml:id="subsec-Introduction-clap">
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <p>
      In this smart world, home automation is a prominent area where smart technology plays a major role in accessing our home appliances. In this experiment you will know how home automation plays a significant role and also will believe learners will have a huge impact about home automation. This experiment is a simple and renewable prototype for home automation which activates on/off the light automatically based on the clap sound.  It acts as helping aid for differently abled people to access their electrical appliances in their home or workplace. Automatic clapper is a machine which controls the light by making any sound. It can be used to on/off light without any human intervention. It is much useful for differently abled people to access their electrical appliances without any hindrances. It can be effectively used in home, offices and college.
    </p>
  </subsection>
